snippet.title: Crayola Magic Wardrobe Demo Gameplay
snippet.description:
IBM brings you Crayola Magic Wardrobe (Demo). With this software young girls can read and write diaries, visit 12 historical periods and hear cool historical facts, color and decorate period costumes using 71 crayola colors and 84 stamps and more for hours of creative learning. 

TSM Channel on Facebook : https://fb.me/tsmchannel
TSM Channel on STEAM : http://steamcommunity.com/groups/tsmchannel
TSM Channel on Google+ : https://google.com/+TSMChannel
TSM Channel on Blogger : http://tsmchannel.blogspot.com
